parameters:
Passerby: Hey, do you know? I heard that the real name of
Duke Shark is Memimi Sameyama. She's apparently the student
council president at Doritoku Academy.

Passerby: To think her true identity is the uptight student
council president, it really fits her haughty character. To
be such a beauty and an elite of the academy, I'm truly
impressed.

Passerby: What's that noise over there? It's coming from the
direction of the Monster Fight arena... But there wasn't
supposed to be a match today...

Memimi: Ugh... Again, people... Wandering around the
underground city in the middle of the day... Idle fools...

Passerby: Whoa, Duke Shark is parading through the
underground city completely naked and masturbating!!

Passerby: What is this, a dream!? What a vulgar act... Oh
my...!

Memimi: (Stop making such a fuss...! I've been seen again...
By now, over 100 people have witnessed me like this...
Eek...!)

Memimi, spurred on by the Anomalocaris-like men, obediently
spreads her legs wide, fondling her breasts and pussy as she
slowly strides down the middle of the road...

Naturally, her figure draws the gaze of everyone on the
street, plunging the young girl into a whirlwind of shame.
If not for Memimi's strong mental fortitude, she would have
fainted from embarrassment and failed the challenge long
ago.

Memimi: Maintain sanity... Stay calm, stay calm...! No
matter who sees me, my spirit will not break...!
